title: Victor Garber ties knot with longtime partner Rainer Andreesen
text:
*Washington D.C., Oct.13 (ANI): Victor Garber and Rainer Andreesen, who have been together for 16 years, have recently tied the knot.*
Washington D.C., Oct.13 (ANI): Victor Garber and Rainer Andreesen, who have been together for 16 years, have recently tied the knot. The artist took to his Instagram page to announce the wedding news and shared the pic which shows him and the 66-year-old actor giggling while posing for camera, E! Online reports. Andreesen captioned the pic, "YES WE DID! #justgotmarried #elopedintofino #canada @therealvictorgarber #after16years." Congratulating the couple , the 'Bravo's Watch What Happens Live' host Andy Cohen wrote "OH MY GOD!!! Much love to you both Mazels all around! Kiss Vic for me!!!" Rosie O'Donnell tweeted, "Congrats to u 2 talented handsome men !!!! Further details of the couple's wedding are yet to be revealed.(ANI) Â»
